#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:3
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "快速上手"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:6
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:8
msgid "For x86 Linux,"
msgstr "x64 Linux"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:10
msgid "``pip install tensorcircuit-ng``"
msgstr "``pip install tensorcircuit-ng``"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:12
msgid "is in general enough."
msgstr "通常情况下已经足够。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:14
msgid ""
"Since there are many optional packages for various features, the users "
"may need to install more packages by pip when required."
msgstr "由于各种功能有很多可选包，用户在需要时可能需要通过 pip 安装更多包。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:17
msgid ""
"For Nvidia GPU, please refer to the GPU aware installation guide of "
"corresponding machine learning frameworks: `TensorFlow "
"<https://www.tensorflow.org/install/pip>`_ (``pip install 'tensorflow"
"[and-cuda]'``), `Jax <https://docs.jax.dev/en/latest/installation.html"
"#pip-installation-nvidia-gpu-cuda-installed-via-pip-easier>`_ (``pip "
"install 'jax[cuda-12]'``), or `PyTorch <https://pytorch.org/get-"
"started/locally/>`_."
msgstr "对于 Nvidia GPU，请参考相应机器学习框架的 GPU 感知安装指南： `TensorFlow <https://www.tensorflow.org/install/pip>`_ (``pip install 'tensorflow[and-cuda]'``), `Jax <https://docs.jax.dev/en/latest/installation.html#pip-installation-nvidia-gpu-cuda-installed-via-pip-easier>`_ (``pip install 'jax[cuda-12]'``), 或 `PyTorch <https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/>`_ 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:24
msgid ""
"Overall, the installation of TensorCircuit-NG is simple, since it is "
"purely in Python and hence portable. As long as the users can take care "
"of the installation of ML frameworks on the corresponding operating "
"system, TensorCircuit-NG will work as expected."
msgstr "总的来说，TensorCircuit-NG 的安装非常简单，因为它纯粹由 Python 编写，因此具有良好的可移植性。只要用户能够在相应的操作系统上完成机器学习框架的安装，TensorCircuit-NG 就能按预期工作。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:27
msgid ""
"To debug the installation issue or report bugs, please check the "
"environment information by ``tc.about()``."
msgstr "要调试安装问题或报告错误，请通过 ``tc.about()`` 检查环境信息。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:30
msgid ""
"We also provide a nightly build of tensorcircuit via PyPI which can be "
"accessed by ``pip uninstall tensorcircuit-ng``, then ``pip install "
"tensorcircuit-nightly``"
msgstr "我们还通过 PyPI 提供 tensorcircuit 的每日构建版本，可通过以下命令访问： ``pip uninstall tensorcircuit-ng`` ，然后 ``pip install tensorcircuit-nightly``"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:35
msgid ""
"**AI-Native Development:** We highly recommend developing with AI coding "
"agents (e.g., Cursor, Claude Code, Gemini CLI) directly within the cloned"
" repository to leverage the rich context from examples and tests. See "
":doc:`agentic` for details."
msgstr "**AI 原生开发：** 我们强烈建议直接在克隆的仓库中使用 AI 编程助手（如 Cursor、Claude Code、Gemini CLI）进行开发，以利用来自示例和测试的丰富上下文。详见 :doc:`agentic` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:39
msgid "Circuit Object"
msgstr "电路对象"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:41
msgid "The basic object for TensorCircuit-NG is ``tc.Circuit``."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 的基本对象是 ``tc.Circuit`` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:43
msgid "Initialize the circuit with the number of qubits ``c=tc.Circuit(n)``."
msgstr "用量子比特数(n) ``c=tc.Circuit(n)`` 来初始化电路。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:45
msgid "**Input States:**"
msgstr "**输入状态：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:47
msgid ""
"The default input function for the circuit is :math:`\\vert 0^n "
"\\rangle`. One can change this to other wavefunctions by directly feeding"
" the inputs state vectors w: ``c=tc.Circuit(n, inputs=w)``."
msgstr ""
"电路的默认输入函数是 :math:`\\vert 0^n \\rangle` 。可以通过直接输入输入状态向量 w 将其更改为其他波函数: "
"``c=tc.Circuit(n, inputs=w)``。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:49
msgid ""
"One can also feed matrix product states as input states for the circuit, "
"but we leave MPS/MPO usage for future sections."
msgstr "也可以将矩阵乘积状态作为电路的输入状态，但我们将矩阵乘积状态/矩阵乘积算子的使用留待后续讲解。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:51
msgid "**Quantum Gates:**"
msgstr "**量子门：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:53
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"We can apply gates on circuit objects. For example, using ``c.H(1)`` or "
"``c.rx(2, theta=0.2)``, we can apply Hadamard gate on qubit 1 (0-based) "
"or apply Rx gate on qubit 2 as :math:`e^{-i\\theta/2 X}`."
msgstr ""
"我们可以将门应用于电路对象。 例如，使用 ``c.H(1)`` 或 ``c.rx(2, theta=0.2)``，我们可以将 Hadamard "
"门应用于量子比特1 （基于0）或将 Rx 门应用于量子比特2 :math:`e^{-i\\theta/2 X}`。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:55
msgid "The same rule also applies to multi-qubit gates, such as ``c.cnot(0, 1)``."
msgstr "同样的规则亦适用于多量子比特门，例如  ``c.cnot(0, 1)`` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:57
msgid "There are also highly customizable gates, two instances are:"
msgstr "这些量子门也是高度可定制的，下面是两个例子"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:59
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``c.exp1(0, 1, unitary=m, theta=0.2)`` which is for the exponential gate "
":math:`e^{i\\theta m}` of any matrix m as long as :math:`m^2=1`."
msgstr ""
"``c.exp1(0, 1, unitary=m, theta=0.2)`` 用于任何矩阵 m 的指数门 :math:`e^{i\\theta "
"m}`，只要 m 满足 :math:`m^2=1`。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:61
msgid ""
"``c.any(0, 1, unitary=m)`` which is for applying the unitary gate m on "
"the circuit."
msgstr "``c.any(0, 1, unitary=m)`` 在电路上作用任意的幺正量子门。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:63
msgid "These two examples are flexible and support gates on any number of qubits."
msgstr "这两个例子很灵活，支持任意数量的量子比特上的门。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:65
msgid "**Measurements and Expectations:**"
msgstr "**测量与期望：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:67
msgid ""
"The most straightforward way to get the output from the circuit object is"
" by getting the output wavefunction in vector form as ``c.state()``."
msgstr "从电路对象中获取输出的最直接的方法是通过 ``c.state()`` 以向量形式获取输出波函数。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:69
msgid ""
"For bitstring sampling, we have ``c.perfect_sampling()`` which returns "
"the bitstring and the corresponding probability amplitude."
msgstr "对于位串采样，我们有 ``c.perfect_sampling()`` ，它返回位串和相应的概率幅度。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:71
msgid ""
"To measure part of the qubits, we can use ``c.measure(0, 1)``, if we want"
" to know the corresponding probability of the measurement output, try "
"``c.measure(0, 1, with_prob=True)``. The measure API is by default non-"
"jittable, but we also have a jittable version as ``c.measure_jit(0, 1)``."
msgstr ""
"要测量部分量子比特，我们可以使用 ``c.measure(0, 1)``，如果我们想知道测量的结果的对应概率，可以尝试 "
"``c.measure(0, 1, with_prob=True)``。 测量 API 在默认情况下是不可即时编译的 "
"，但我们也有一个可即时编译的版本，如 ``c.measure_jit(0, 1)``。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:73
msgid ""
"The measurement and sampling utilize advanced algorithms based on "
"tensornetwork and thus require no knowledge or space for the full "
"wavefunction."
msgstr "测量和采样使用了基于张量网络的高级算法，因此不需要任何相关知识或者空间来获取全波函数。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:75
msgid "See the example below:"
msgstr "请看下面的例子："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:93
msgid ""
"To compute expectation values for local observables, we have "
"``c.expectation([tc.gates.z(), [0]], [tc.gates.z(), [1]])`` for "
":math:`\\langle Z_0Z_1 \\rangle` or ``c.expectation([tc.gates.x(), "
"[0]])`` for :math:`\\langle X_0 \\rangle`."
msgstr ""
"为了计算局部可观察量的期望值，我们有 ``c.expectation([tc.gates.z(), [0]], [tc.gates.z(), "
"[1]])`` 对应的期望为 :math:`\\langle Z_0Z_1 \\rangle` 时，或 "
"``c.expectation([tc.gates.x(), [0]])`` 对应的期望为 :math:`\\langle X_0 "
"\\rangle`时."

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:95
msgid ""
"This expectation API is rather flexible, as one can measure an m on "
"several qubits as ``c.expectation([m, [0, 1, 2]])``."
msgstr "因为可以在几个量子比特上测量一个 m，这种计算期望值的 API 相当灵活： ``c.expectation([m, [0, 1, 2]])`` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:97
msgid ""
"We can also extract the unitary matrix underlying the whole circuit as "
"follows:"
msgstr "我们还可以提取整个电路对应的幺正矩阵，如下所示："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:110
msgid "**Circuit Transformations:**"
msgstr "**电路转换：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:112
msgid ""
"We currently support transform ``tc.Circuit`` from and to Qiskit "
"``QuantumCircuit`` object."
msgstr "我们目前支持 ``tc.Circuit`` 与 Qiskit ``QuantumCircuit`` 对象之间的互相转换。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:114
msgid ""
"Export to Qiskit (possible for further hardware experiment, compiling, "
"and visualization): ``c.to_qiskit()``."
msgstr "导出到 Qiskit（可能用于进一步的硬件实验、编译和可视化）： ``c.to_qiskit()`` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:116
msgid ""
"Import from Qiskit: ``c = tc.Circuit.from_qiskit(QuantumCircuit, n)``. "
"Parameterized Qiskit circuit is supported by passing the parameters to "
"the ``binding_parameters`` argument of the ``from_qiskit`` function, "
"similar to the ``assign_parameters`` function in Qiskit."
msgstr "从 Qiskit 导入： ``c = tc.Circuit.from_qiskit(QuantumCircuit, n)`` 。通过将参数传递给 ``from_qiskit`` 函数的 ``binding_parameters`` 参数，可以支持参数化的 Qiskit 线路，类似于 Qiskit 中的 ``assign_parameters`` 函数。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:120
msgid "**Circuit Visualization:**"
msgstr "**电路可视化：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:122
msgid ""
"``c.vis_tex()`` can generate tex code for circuit visualization based on "
"LaTeX `quantikz <https://arxiv.org/abs/1809.03842>`__ package."
msgstr ""
"``c.vis_tex()`` 可以基于  `quantikz <https://arxiv.org/abs/1809.03842>`__ "
"package 生成用于电路可视化的 tex 代码。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:124
msgid ""
"There are also some automatic pipeline helper functions to directly "
"generate figures from tex code, but they require extra installations in "
"the environment."
msgstr "还有一些自动辅助函数可以直接从 tex 代码生成图形，但它们需要在环境中进行额外安装。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:126
msgid ""
"``render_pdf(tex)`` function requires full installation of LaTeX locally."
" And in the Jupyter environment, we may prefer ``render_pdf(tex, "
"notebook=True)`` to return jpg figures, which further require wand "
"magicwand library installed, see `here <https://docs.wand-"
"py.org/en/latest/>`__."
msgstr ""
"``render_pdf(tex)`` 函数需要在本地完全安装 LaTeX。 在 Jupyter 环境中，我们可能会偏好 "
"``render_pdf(tex, notebook=True)`` 来返回 jpg 图形，这需要安装 wand magicwand 库，请参阅 "
"`这里 <https://docs.wand-py.org/en/latest/>`__ 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:128
msgid ""
"Or since we can transform ``tc.Circuit`` into QuantumCircuit easily, we "
"have a simple pipeline to first transform ``tc.Circuit`` into Qiskit and "
"then call the visualization built in Qiskit. Namely, we have ``c.draw()``"
" API."
msgstr ""
"或者因为我们可以轻松地将 ``tc.Circuit`` 转换为 QuantumCircuit，我们有一个简单的管道来首先转换 "
"``tc.Circuit`` 为 Qiskit，然后调用 Qiskit 中内置的可视化。 也就是说，我们有 ``c.draw()`` API。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:130
msgid "**Circuit Intermediate Representation:**"
msgstr "**电路中间表示：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:132
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG provides its own circuit IR as a python list of dicts. "
"This IR can be further utilized to run compiling, generate serialization "
"qasm, or render circuit figures."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 提供自己的中间表示是元素是字典的列表。此中间表示可进一步用于运行编译、生成序列化 qasm 或渲染电路图。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:134
msgid ""
"The IR is given as a list, each element is a dict containing information "
"on one gate that is applied to the circuit. Note gate attr in the dict is"
" a python function that returns the gate's node."
msgstr ""
"中间表示以列表形式给出，每个元素都是一个字典，其中包含应用于电路的一个量子门的信息。 注意字典中的 gate atrr "
"实际上是一个返回此量子门的节点的 python 函数。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:144
msgid ""
"We can also create new copied circuit via ``c.copy()`` which internally "
"utilize the ``qir``."
msgstr "我们还可以通过 ``c.copy()`` 创建新的复制线路，其内部利用了 ``qir`` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:148
msgid "Programming Paradigm"
msgstr "编程范式"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:150
msgid ""
"The most common case and the most typical programming paradigm for "
"TensorCircuit-NG are to evaluate the circuit output and the corresponding"
" quantum gradients, which is common in variational quantum algorithms."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 最常见的情况和最典型的编程范式是评估电路的输出以及相应的量子梯度，这在变分量子算法中很常见。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:177
msgid ""
"Also for a non-quantum example (linear regression) demonstrating the "
"backend agnostic feature, variables with pytree support, AD/jit/vmap "
"usage, and variational optimization loops. Please refer to the example "
"script: `linear regression example <https://github.com/tensorcircuit"
"/tensorcircuit-ng/blob/master/examples/universal_lr.py>`_. This example "
"might be more friendly to the machine learning community since it is "
"purely classical while also showcasing the main features and paradigms of"
" tensorcircuit-ng."
msgstr ""
"同样对于演示后端不可知特性的非量子示例（线性回归），pytree 支持变量、自动微分/即时编译/矢量并行化 用法和变分优化循环。请参考示例脚本: "
"`线性回归示例 <https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng/blob/master/examples/universal_lr.py>`_ 。 "
"这个例子可能对机器学习的用户更友好，因为它纯粹是经典的，同时也展示了 TensorCircuit-NG 的主要特征和范式。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:180
msgid ""
"If the user has no intention to maintain the application code in a "
"backend agnostic fashion, the API for ML frameworks can be more handily "
"used and interleaved with the TensorCircuit-NG API."
msgstr ""
"如果用户无意以与后端无关的方式维护应用程序代码，则可以更方便地使用用于机器学习框架的 API 并将其与 TensorCircuit-NG API "
"交替使用。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:215
msgid "Automatic Differentiation, JIT, and Vectorized Parallelism"
msgstr "自动微分、即时编译和矢量化并行 "

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:217
msgid ""
"For concepts of AD, JIT and VMAP, please refer to `Jax documentation "
"<https://docs.jax.dev/en/latest/tutorials.html>`__ ."
msgstr ""
"关于自动微分、即时编译和向量并行化，请参考 `Jax 文档 "
"<https://docs.jax.dev/en/latest/tutorials.html>`__ 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:219
msgid ""
"The related API design in TensorCircuit-NG closely follows the functional"
" programming design pattern in Jax with some slight differences. So we "
"strongly recommend users learn some basics about Jax no matter which ML "
"backend they intend to use."
msgstr ""
"TensorCircuit-NG 中的相关 API 设计与 Jax 中的函数式编程的设计模式密切相关，但是略有不同。因此，我们强烈建议用户学习一些有关 "
"Jax 的基础知识，无论他们打算使用哪种机器学习后端。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:221
msgid "**AD Support:**"
msgstr "**自动微分（AD）支持：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:223
msgid ""
"Automatic Differentiation (AD) is crucial for quantum circuit "
"optimization. TensorCircuit-NG supports various differentiation "
"operations:"
msgstr "自动微分（AD）对于量子线路优化至关重要。TensorCircuit-NG 支持各种微分操作："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:225
msgid "Gradients: First-order derivatives"
msgstr "梯度：一阶导数"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:226
msgid "Vector-Jacobian products (vjps): Efficient backward-mode differentiation"
msgstr "向量-雅可比积（vjps）：高效的反向模式微分"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:227
msgid "Jacobian-vector products (jvps): Efficient forward-mode differentiation"
msgstr "雅可比-向量积（jvps）：高效的前向模式微分"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:228
msgid "Natural gradients: Geometry-aware optimization"
msgstr "自然梯度：几何感知优化"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:229
msgid "Jacobians: Full derivative matrices"
msgstr "雅可比矩阵：全导数矩阵"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:230
msgid "Hessians: Second-order derivatives"
msgstr "海森矩阵：二阶导数"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:232
msgid "Example of gradient computation:"
msgstr "梯度计算示例："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:256
msgid "**JIT Support:**"
msgstr "**即时编译（JIT）支持：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:258
msgid ""
"Just-In-Time (JIT) compilation significantly accelerates quantum circuit "
"simulation by optimizing the computation graph. Key points:"
msgstr "即时编译（JIT）通过优化计算图显著加速量子线路模拟。关键点："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:260
msgid "Use JIT for functions that will be called multiple times"
msgstr "对将被多次调用的函数使用 JIT"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:261
msgid ""
"JIT compilation has some overhead, so it's most beneficial for repeated "
"executions"
msgstr "JIT 编译有一定的开销，因此对于重复执行最有益"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:262
msgid "Ensure input shapes and types are consistent to avoid recompilation"
msgstr "确保输入形状和类型一致，以避免重新编译"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:263
msgid ""
"The input and output of the functions are all tensors, except static "
"inputs."
msgstr "除了静态输入外，函数的输入和输出都是张量。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:265
msgid "Example of JIT acceleration:"
msgstr "JIT 加速示例："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:291
msgid "**VMAP Support:**"
msgstr "**VMAP 支持：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:293
msgid ""
"Vectorized mapping (vmap) enables parallel evaluation across multiple "
"inputs or parameters:"
msgstr "向量化映射（vmap）支持跨多个输入或参数的并行评估："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:295
msgid "Batch processing of quantum circuit input wavefunctions"
msgstr "量子线路输入波函数的批处理"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:296
msgid "Batch processing quantum circuit structure"
msgstr "量子线路结构的批处理"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:297
msgid "Parallel parameter optimization"
msgstr "并行参数优化"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:298
msgid "Efficient Monte Carlo sampling for noise simulation"
msgstr "噪声模拟的高效蒙特卡洛采样"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:299
msgid "Vectorized measurement operations"
msgstr "向量化测量操作"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:301
msgid "Example of vmap for parallel circuit evaluation:"
msgstr "并行线路评估的 vmap 示例："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:320
msgid ""
"For more advanced usage patterns and detailed examples of vmap, refer to "
"our `vmap tutorial <https://tensorcircuit-"
"ng.readthedocs.io/en/latest/whitepaper/6-3-vmap.html>`_."
msgstr "有关 vmap 的更多高级用法模式和详细示例，请参阅我们的 `vmap 教程 <https://tensorcircuit-ng.readthedocs.io/en/latest/whitepaper/6-3-vmap.html>`_ 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:324
msgid "Backend Agnosticism"
msgstr "后端无关特性"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:326
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG supports TensorFlow, Jax, and PyTorch backends. We "
"recommend using TensorFlow or Jax backend since PyTorch lacks advanced "
"jit and vmap features."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 支持 TensorFlow、Jax 和 PyTorch 后端。 我们建议使用 TensorFlow 或 Jax 后端，因为 PyTorch 缺乏高级 jit 和 vmap 功能。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:328
msgid ""
"The backend can be set as ``K=tc.set_backend(\"jax\")`` and ``K`` is the "
"backend with a full set of APIs as a conventional ML framework, which can"
" also be accessed by ``tc.backend``."
msgstr ""
"后端可以设置为 ``K=tc.set_backend(\"jax\")`` ，``K``作为常规机器学习框架的全套API的后端，也可以通过``tc"
" .backend`` 被访问。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:351
msgid ""
"The supported APIs in the backend come from two sources, one part is "
"implemented in `TensorNetwork package "
"<https://github.com/google/TensorNetwork/blob/master/tensornetwork/backends/abstract_backend.py>`__"
" and the other part is implemented in `TensorCircuit-NG package "
"<modules.html#module-tensorcircuit.backends>`__. To see all the backend "
"agnostic APIs, try:"
msgstr "在后端支持的 APIs 有两个来源 , 一个来自 `TensorNetwork <https://github.com/google/TensorNetwork/blob/master/tensornetwork/backends/abstract_backend.py>`__ 另一个来自 `TensorCircuit-NG package <modules.html#module-tensorcircuit.backends>`__。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:360
msgid "Working with Data Types (Dtype)"
msgstr "使用数据类型 (Dtype)"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:362
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG supports numerical simulation with both **32-bit** "
"(default) and **64-bit** precision. You can switch the global precision "
"using ``tc.set_dtype``."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 支持 **32 位 ** （默认）和 **64 位** 精度的数值模拟。您可以使用 ``tc.set_dtype`` 切换全局精度。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:375
msgid ""
"The following properties provide strings for the currently active data "
"types:"
msgstr "以下属性提供了当前活动数据类型的字符串："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:377
msgid ""
"``tc.dtypestr``: The complex data type (e.g., ``\"complex64\"`` or "
"``\"complex128\"``)."
msgstr "``tc.dtypestr`` ：复数数据类型（例如 ``\"complex64\"`` 或 ``\"complex128\"`` ）。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:378
msgid ""
"``tc.rdtypestr``: The corresponding real data type (e.g., ``\"float32\"``"
" or ``\"float64\"``)."
msgstr "``tc.rdtypestr`` ：相应的实数数据类型（例如 ``\"float32\"`` 或 ``\"float64\"`` ）。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:379
msgid ""
"``tc.idtypestr``: The corresponding integer data type (e.g., "
"``\"int32\"`` or ``\"int64\"``)."
msgstr "``tc.idtypestr`` ：相应的整数数据类型（例如 ``\"int32\"`` 或 ``\"int64\"`` ）。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:383
msgid "Setup the Contractor"
msgstr "设置 contractor"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:385
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG is a tensornetwork contraction-based quantum circuit "
"simulator. A contractor is for searching for the optimal contraction path"
" of the circuit tensornetwork."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 是一个基于张量网络收缩的量子线路模拟器。 contractor 用于搜索电路张量网络的最佳收缩路径。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:387
msgid ""
"There are various advanced contractors provided by third-party packages, "
"such as `opt-einsum <https://github.com/dgasmith/opt_einsum>`__ and "
"`cotengra <https://github.com/jcmgray/cotengra>`__."
msgstr ""
"有各种第三方包提供的高级 contractor ，例如 `opt-einsum "
"<https://github.com/dgasmith/opt_einsum>`__ 和 `cotengra "
"<https://github.com/jcmgray/cotengra>`__ 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:389
msgid ""
"`opt-einsum` is shipped with TensorNetwork package. To use cotengra, one "
"needs to pip install it; kahypar is also recommended to install with "
"cotengra."
msgstr ""
"`opt-einsum` 随 TensorNetwork 软件包一起。如要使用 cotengra，则需要 pip 安装它； 还建议安装 "
"cotengra 随 kahypar 一起使用。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:391
msgid "Some setup cases:"
msgstr "一些设置案例："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:417
msgid ""
"For advanced configurations on cotengra contractors, please refer to "
"cotengra `doc "
"<https://cotengra.readthedocs.io/en/latest/advanced.html>`__ ."
msgstr "有关 cotengra contractor 的高级配置，请参阅 cotengra `文档 <https://cotengra.readthedocs.io/en/latest/advanced.html>`__ 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:419
msgid "**Setup in Function or Context Level**"
msgstr "**函数和上下文级别的设置**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:421
msgid ""
"Beside global level setup, we can also setup the backend, the dtype, and "
"the contractor at the function level or context manager level:"
msgstr "除了全局级别设置，我们还可以在函数级别或上下文管理器级别设置后端、dtype 和contractor："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:439
msgid "Noisy Circuit Simulation"
msgstr "噪声电路模拟"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:441
msgid "**Monte Carlo State Simulator:**"
msgstr "**蒙特卡洛态模拟器**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:443
msgid ""
"For the Monte Carlo trajectory noise simulator, the unitary Kraus channel"
" can be handled easily. TensorCircuit-NG also supports fully jittable and"
" differentiable general Kraus channel Monte Carlo simulation, though."
msgstr "对于蒙特卡洛轨迹噪声模拟器，可以轻松处理幺正的 Kraus 通道。 不过，TensorCircuit-NG 还支持完全可即时编译和可微分的通用 Kraus 通道蒙特卡罗模拟。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:470
msgid "**Density Matrix Simulator:**"
msgstr "**密度矩阵模拟器**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:472
msgid ""
"Density matrix simulator ``tc.DMCircuit`` simulates the noise in a full "
"form, but takes twice qubits to do noiseless simulation. The API is the "
"same as ``tc.Circuit``."
msgstr "密度矩阵模拟器 ``tc.DMCircuit`` 以完整形式模拟噪声，但需要两倍的量子比特。API 与 ``tc.Circuit`` 基本相同。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:491
msgid "**Experiment with quantum errors:**"
msgstr "**量子误差实验：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:493
msgid "Multiple quantum errors can be added on circuit."
msgstr "可以在线路上添加多种量子误差。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:509
msgid "**Experiment with readout error:**"
msgstr "**读取误差实验：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:511
msgid ""
"Readout error can be added in experiments for sampling and expectation "
"value calculation."
msgstr "可以在采样和期望值计算的实验中添加读取误差。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:537
msgid "MPS and MPO"
msgstr "矩阵乘积状态和矩阵乘积算子"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:539
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG has its class for MPS and MPO originally defined in "
"TensorNetwork as ``tc.QuVector``, ``tc.QuOperator``."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 有自己的 MPS 和 MPO 类，起初在 TensorNetwork 中定义为 ``tc.QuVector`` 和 ``tc.QuOperator`` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:541
msgid ""
"``tc.QuVector`` can be extracted from ``tc.Circuit`` as the tensor "
"network form for the output state (uncontracted) by ``c.quvector()``."
msgstr ""
"作为``c.quvector()`` 的输出状态（未收缩）的张量网络形式，``tc.QuVector`` 可以从``tc.Circuit`` "
"中提取。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:543
msgid ""
"The QuVector forms a wavefunction w, which can also be fed into Circuit "
"as the inputs state as ``c=tc.Circuit(n, mps_inputs=w)``."
msgstr ""
"QuVector 形成一个波函数 w，它也可以作为 ``c=tc.Circuit(n, mps_inputs=w)`` 的输入状态输入到 "
"Circuit 中。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:545
msgid "MPS as input state for circuit"
msgstr "MPS 作为电路的输入状态"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:547
msgid ""
"The MPS/QuVector representation of the input state has a more efficient "
"and compact form."
msgstr "输入状态的 MPS/QuVector 表示具有更高效和紧凑的形式。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:559
msgid "MPS as (uncomputed) output state for circuit"
msgstr "MPS 作为电路的（未计算的）输出状态"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:561
msgid ""
"For example, a quick way to calculate the wavefunction overlap without "
"explicitly computing the state amplitude is given as below:"
msgstr "例如，在不显式计算状态幅度的情况下，计算波函数重叠的快速方法如下："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:578
msgid "MPO as the gate on the circuit"
msgstr "MPO 作为电路上的门"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:580
msgid ""
"Instead of a common quantum gate in matrix/node format, we can directly "
"apply a gate in MPO/QuOperator format."
msgstr "代替矩阵/节点格式的普通量子门，我们可以直接应用 MPO/QuOperator 格式的门。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:591
msgid ""
"The representative gate defined in MPO format is the ``multicontrol`` "
"gate."
msgstr "以 MPO 格式定义的代表门是 ``multicontrol`` 门。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:593
msgid "MPO as the operator for expectation evaluation on a circuit"
msgstr "MPO作为电路期望估测算子"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:595
msgid ""
"We can also measure operator expectation on the circuit output state "
"where the operator is in MPO/QuOperator format."
msgstr "我们还可以测量运算符对 MPO/QuOperator 格式的电路输出状态的期望。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:607
msgid "Interfaces"
msgstr "接口"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:609
msgid "**PyTorch Interface to Hybrid with PyTorch Modules:**"
msgstr "**与 PyTorch 模块混合的 PyTorch 接口：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:611
msgid ""
"As we have mentioned in the backend section, the PyTorch backend may lack"
" advanced features. This doesn't mean we cannot hybrid the advanced "
"circuit module with PyTorch neural module. We can run the quantum "
"function on TensorFlow or Jax backend while wrapping it with a Torch "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"正如我们在后端部分提到的，PyTorch 后端可能缺少高级功能。 这并不意味着我们不能将高级量子电路模块与 PyTorch 神经模块混合。 "
"我们可以在 TensorFlow 或 Jax 后端运行量子函数，同时使用 Torch 接口包装它。 "

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:638
msgid ""
"For a GPU/CPU, torch/tensorflow, quantum/classical hybrid machine "
"learning pipeline enabled by tensorcircuit, see `example script "
"<https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-"
"ng/blob/master/examples/hybrid_gpu_pipeline.py>`__."
msgstr "对于由 tensorcircuit 支持的 GPU/CPU、torch/tensorflow、量子/经典混合机器学习流水线，请参见 `示例脚本 <https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng/blob/master/examples/hybrid_gpu_pipeline.py>`__。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:640
msgid ""
"There is also a more flexible torch interface that support static non-"
"tensor inputs as keyword arguments, which can be utilized as below:"
msgstr "还有一个更灵活的 torch 接口，支持将静态非张量输入作为关键字参数，用法如下："

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:654
msgid ""
"We also provider wrapper of quantum function for torch module as "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.TorchLayer` alias to "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.torchnn.QuantumNet`."
msgstr "我们还为 torch 模块提供了量子函数的包装器，如 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.TorchLayer` ，它是 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.torchnn.QuantumNet` 的别名。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:656
msgid ""
"For ``TorchLayer``, ``use_interface=True`` is by default, which natively "
"allow the quantum function defined on other tensorcircuit backends, such "
"as jax or tf for speed consideration."
msgstr "对于 ``TorchLayer`` ，默认情况下 ``use_interface=True`` ，这原生允许在其他 tensorcircuit 后端（如 jax 或 tf）上定义的量子函数，以考虑速度。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:658
msgid ""
"``TorchLayer`` can process multiple input arguments as multiple function "
"inputs, following torch practice."
msgstr "``TorchLayer`` 可以按照 torch 的惯例，将多个输入参数处理为多个函数输入。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:686
msgid "**TensorFlow interfaces:**"
msgstr "**TensorFlow 接口：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:688
msgid ""
"Similar rules apply similar as torch interface. The interface can even be"
" used within jit environment outside. See "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.interfaces.tensorflow.tensorflow_interface`."
msgstr "类似于 torch 接口的规则也适用。该接口甚至可以在外部的 jit 环境中使用。参见 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.interfaces.tensorflow.tensorflow_interface` 。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:691
msgid ""
"We also provider ``enable_dlpack=True`` option in torch and tf "
"interfaces, which allow the tensor transformation happen without memory "
"transfer via dlpack, higher version of tf or torch package required."
msgstr "我们还在 torch 和 tf 接口中提供了 ``enable_dlpack=True`` 选项，允许在不通过 dlpack 进行内存传输的情况下进行张量转换，需要更高版本的 tf 或 torch 包。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:694
msgid ""
"We also provider wrapper of quantum function for keras layer as "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.KerasLayer` alias to "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.keras.KerasLayer`."
msgstr "我们还为 keras 层提供了量子函数的包装器，如 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.KerasLayer` ，它是 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.keras.KerasLayer` 的别名。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:696
msgid ""
"``KerasLayer`` can process multiple input arguments with the input as a "
"dict, following the common keras practice, see example below."
msgstr "``KerasLayer`` 可以按照通用的 keras 惯例，将输入作为字典处理多个输入参数，参见下面的示例。"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:716
msgid "**JAX interfaces:**"
msgstr "**JAX 接口：**"

#: ../../source/quickstart.rst:718
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG also newly introduces JAX interface to seamlessly "
"integrate with JAX's ecosystem. This allows you to use JAX's powerful "
"features like automatic differentiation, JIT compilation, and "
"vectorization with quantum circuits or functions running on any backend."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 最近还引入了 JAX 接口，以无缝集成到 JAX 的生态系统中。这允许您在任何后端上运行的量子线路或函数中使用 JAX 的强大功能，如自动微分、JIT 编译和向量化。"

